data.description: Welcome to this beautiful renovated home! It gives the best blend between a home style and comfort living making it the ideal place to create lasting memories. Some of the many upgrades done to this charming home are new recent interior paint throughout, brand new ceramic tile in the kitchen, dinning, bathrooms and entrance; also recently installed are the baseboards and recessed lighting. Furnace replaced less than 2 years ago. Located on East Sparks and only 4 minutes away to the Legends Shopping Mall! The renovated kitchen features an upgraded hardwood butcher countertops that offers the natural beauty of wood while offering an exceptional look to your kitchen. You'll also find a newly installed deep stainless steel kitchen sink and faucet. As you walk in you'll noticed vaulted ceilings with an inviting floorplan while enjoying the convenient location of this home. This is a beautiful home you won't want to miss out on!
